cienaWsChassisMIB.name: cienaWsChassisMIB

revisions.description: Waveserver Release 1.5 Added ncx:user-write to 'power-supply-units', 'cooling-fan-units', and 'management-port'.
Waveserver Rel 1.4 revision. New ciena-ws-encryption.yang now contains augments for the chassis container. Aligned MIB files to respect YANG read/write status.
Waveserver Rel 1.3 revised. Added leaf 'package-serial-number', 'package-part-number, and 'leaf package-revision' to 'device-id' container.
Waveserver Rel 1.2 revised. Major restructuring of this YANG module.
Waveserver Rel 1.1 revised. Added 'management-port' container and related leafs. Deleted the 'temperature-sensor-status' list.
